{"tid":1439903,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[如何分辨鬼］入嚟放低一個前線撞鬼經驗！","createTime":"2019-08-10T09:09:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T03:46:50.000Z","uid":88177,"like":130,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"818ccfa9c67af359fb90b0f5c53d8637c800daac","tid":1439903,"uid":88177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T09:09:59.000Z","msg":"之前有試過撞鬼，通常practice係通常係男，會扮哨兵，戴埋豬嘴，係d狗防線向前推果陣走過黎，每三兩分鐘同你講:<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">&rdquo;啲警察係xx方向黎緊，會包抄你，要走就係後面轉彎走&rdquo;</span></span><br />\n<br />\n之後防線一向前推，鬼就會喺最前，帶着啲人走咗入去旁邊嘅路。佢會喺前面大約一陣，轉個頭你就發現唔見咗人。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果你問佢喂邊度source呀，佢會話係Tg 哨兵站，未經證實消息。試過喺彌敦道，有鬼話啲警察喺土瓜灣方向嚟緊.....遠到仆街。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n上次喺旺角就係有鬼話向九龍城方向跑無事，但係九龍城連地鐵都冇。不過佢都帶走左好多人，最後佢哋就係行到去黃大仙，之後大家知乜事。<br />\n<br />\n經驗總結<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: green;\"><br />\n1. 會話警察由唔同方向嚟緊，包抄緊！<br />\n2. 突然間話要快閃某個地方！仲要係走埋嚟逐個同你講，唔係用大聲公。<br />\n3. 警察防線一推進，會喺最前帶路，大約一個鐘左右就會突然消失！<br />\n4. 通常係男！可能着黑衫，戴豬咀。<br />\n5. 通常出現喺盾陣前面前線！<br />\n6. 可能會show個live地圖出黎，話你知邊道有狗過緊黎！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">放低自己撞鬼經驗，等大家見到！</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf829369167dbf1aff874e101411cd7728e84af1","tid":1439903,"uid":88177,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T09:10:17.000Z","msg":"自推十次"},{"pid":"6582914c19f053a17a6641140e997a76c1fb9edb","tid":1439903,"uid":88177,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T09:10:36.000Z","msg":"九"},{"pid":"6665e3c147cbfd8df0de4c815060dc382ea9e26c","tid":1439903,"uid":88177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T09:10:47.000Z","msg":"八"},{"pid":"9151e28c1eb6e77adc3d242db8285e3c75ebf62e","tid":1439903,"uid":88177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T09:10:58.000Z","msg":"七"},{"pid":"75a641a4455cc8939869b5261f44751ff753f17f","tid":1439903,"uid":88177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T09:11:13.000Z","msg":"六"},{"pid":"6e20442d531ee792b942e554eaccab4161c77c5e","tid":1439903,"uid":50779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T09:11:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"459dd38030cec2856f738cf5d192916f4f7b4bf1","tid":1439903,"uid":88177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T09:11:31.000Z","msg":"五"},{"pid":"0b44b1629fbbefe8fca040e98ea91179cbcc55de","tid":1439903,"uid":88177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T09:11:50.000Z","msg":"四"},{"pid":"3064b4e82992fca76b123088d927e214ef51b276","tid":1439903,"uid":88177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T09:12:09.000Z","msg":"三"},{"pid":"8d53269365bf3dbe8e8b16ad3a06a73b6f4aa343","tid":1439903,"uid":88177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T09:12:20.000Z","msg":"二"},{"pid":"9f189dc5546a19592d2a13746e9754c84d370f92","tid":1439903,"uid":88177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T09:12:30.000Z","msg":"一"},{"pid":"130ee0f9aef2c31c60ba5166512ea782561019a1","tid":1439903,"uid":88177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T09:12:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d61815585c49165632defa4eceef84e328b8fc71","tid":1439903,"uid":99582,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T09:13:07.000Z","msg":"最緊要靠自己熟讀地圖 撚狗係必須 但唔好愈屌愈前"},{"pid":"e422e3a3952b50c638445cbd91c57637f3be93d4","tid":1439903,"uid":3696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T09:13:48.000Z","msg":"緊急！關於港島東反送中反黑大遊行<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1439067\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1439067</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"2cc553e2890544d1191522d0cd02081a3c2ff18f","tid":1439903,"uid":31710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T09:16:39.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n知己知彼"},{"pid":"aa199b209ac941835efae6226ee7b9c52ad4a0d3","tid":1439903,"uid":88177,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d61815585c49165632defa4eceef84e328b8fc71","tid":1439903,"uid":99582,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T09:13:07.000Z","msg":"最緊要靠自己熟讀地圖 撚狗係必須 但唔好愈屌愈前"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T09:16:54.000Z","msg":"啱，但有時無路線，有啲朋友會行得太前。所以發夢嗰陣，要保持理智，千祈唔好啲人講一句，就唔用腦跟。"},{"pid":"e8ef36303d3293acf15d4932405312cef935f276","tid":1439903,"uid":88177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T09:17:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8228174430d00c5b38546ff9585607f9876547d6","tid":1439903,"uid":88177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T09:18:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2e33e3352f0bb2001220f8958095781b6dd2f3d","tid":1439903,"uid":88177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T09:19:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"95b93510ba85e882b088a4be981b06d4196e595f","tid":1439903,"uid":33495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"818ccfa9c67af359fb90b0f5c53d8637c800daac","tid":1439903,"uid":88177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T09:09:59.000Z","msg":"之前有試過撞鬼，通常practice係通常係男，會扮哨兵，戴埋豬嘴，係d狗防線向前推果陣走過黎，每三兩分鐘同你講:<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">&rdquo;啲警察係xx方向黎緊，會包抄你，要走就係後面轉彎走&rdquo;</span></span><br />\n<br />\n之後防線一向前推，鬼就會喺最前，帶着啲人走咗入去旁邊嘅路。佢會喺前面大約一陣，轉個頭你就發現唔見咗人。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果你問佢喂邊度source呀，佢會話係Tg 哨兵站，未經證實消息。試過喺彌敦道，有鬼話啲警察喺土瓜灣方向嚟緊.....遠到仆街。<img s